      "rationale": "The Lacasse et al. (2019) dataset provides inlet flow rates from 2.5 to 6.0 L/min and rotational speeds from 2200 to 4000 RPM with calibrated ultrasonic flow meters (±1.5% FS) and torque sensors. Fluid properties (bovine blood, 37°C) are documented. Conditions are considered representative for validation purposes at MRL 2, though the operating envelope partially extends beyond the CPB range declared in the COU."
